cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image captioning. It also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it generates captions. The paper proposes a new decoding method, which involves masking input sequences, and this falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves multimodality, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
